721873f-a.text:
Nassau Street, east side, from Liberty Street, to Maiden Lane, showing the Federal Reserve Bank building under construction. The photographer is viewing southwestward from a point on Maiden Lane near William Street. Nassau Street is in the right background containing the 31 story Liberty Tower. On the left is the massive N. Y. Mutual Life lInsurance Company building on Liberty Street.
September 15, 1921
